==Japanese==

===Etymology===
From an abbreviation of the English word [[animation]]

===Noun===
'''アニメ''' (animé)
# Animation
#: All animated works are called アニメ in Japan.  In other countries, the romanization [[animé]] is typically used for animation produced primarily for the Japanese market.

